    {
      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, deseed your <strong>peppers</strong> (scrape the seeds and pith out with a teaspoon) and chop into large pieces</p><p>Once softened, add the<strong> chopped pepper</strong> to the pan and cook for 3-4 min further or until the pepper is softened and the beef mince is cooked through (no pink meat!)</p>",
