    {
      "instruction": "<p>While the peppers are cooking, combine your <strong>black bean paste</strong>, <strong>soy sauce </strong>and<strong> </strong>1 tsp <span class=\"text-purple\">[1 1/2 tsp] </span><span class=\"text-danger\">[2 tsp]</span> <strong>sugar</strong> with 150ml<span class=\"text-purple\"> [200ml]<span class=\"text-danger\"> </span>[250ml]</span> <strong>boiled water</strong> – this is your <strong>black bean sauce</strong></p>",
